                    </picture>

                    <p>It’s not possible to have drinks – or a great tailgate for that matter - without a selection of mouth-watering food! The next part of the afternoon saw the bloggers enjoy some tasty treats and gain some creative inspiration for their own tailgate, all provided by
                        <a href="#">Gold Epicure</a>. There was a variety of tacos and a range of tasty burgers for our guests to choose from.</p>

                    <picture>
                        <source data-srcset="./img/webp/trailer-knowledge-details/img-4-min.webp" type="image/webp" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==">
